{"data": [{"id": "4741697", "title": "Loews: Changing My Mind And Raising My Price Target", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture><img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1394094998/image_1394094998.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"A Loews Hotel in Chicago, Illinois, USA.\" data-id=\"1394094998\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1394094998/image_1394094998.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1394094998/image_1394094998.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1394094998/image_1394094998.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1394094998/image_1394094998.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1394094998/image_1394094998.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1394094998/image_1394094998.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1394094998/image_1394094998.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1394094998/image_1394094998.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"></picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-credits\">JHVEPhoto</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>Dear readers/followers,</p> <p>We always want to grow as investors and analysts. I am absolutely no different from anyone here. And while my thesis on <strong>Loews Corporation</strong> (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NYSE:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/L\" title=\"Loews Corporation\">L</a></span>) is actually one of outperformance, meaning my rating has performed in</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1394094998/image_1394094998.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4741697-loews-changing-my-mind-and-raising-my-price-target", "pub_date": "2024-12-03 14:44:05"}, {"id": "4741703", "title": "Enron Is Back From The Dead. Or Is It?", "description": "<div class=\"wsb_wrapper\"> <div class=\"wsb_main\"><span><p class=\"wsb_pb\"><strong>Listen on the go! A daily podcast of Wall Street Breakfast will be available by 8:00 a.m. on <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/author/wall-street-breakfast?utm_source=newsletter&amp;utm_medium=toptext&amp;utm_campaign=wsbpodpromo\">Seeking Alpha</a>, <a href=\"https://podcasts.apple.com/us/podcast/wall-street-breakfast/id1358381502\" rel=\"nofollow\">iTunes</a>, <a href=\"https://open.spotify.com/show/05uLjJxkVgQsRk8LWLCLpx\" rel=\"nofollow\">Spotify</a>.</strong></p></span></div> <figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture><img alt=\"\" data-id=\"674421\" data-type=\"getty-image\" height=\"1265px\" src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/674421/image_674421.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" width=\"1536px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/674421/image_674421.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/674421/image_674421.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/674421/image_674421.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/674421/image_674421.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/674421/image_674421.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/674421/image_674421.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/674421/image_674421.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/674421/image_674421.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"><figcaption><p class=\"item-credits\">Getty Images</p></figcaption></picture></figure><div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div>\n<div class=\"wsb_section\"><div class=\"wsb_mb\"> <p class=\"wsb_pb\"> </p> <p class=\"wsp-pb\"> </p> <h2>Ask Why</h2> <p class=\"wsp-pb\"> </p> <p>It's likely a parody, but is it also a sign of a frothy market as investors close out 2024?<br><br>Enron, the energy firm behind one of the largest corporate scandals in America, has been brought <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/news/4357638-scam-parody-sign-of-a-top-enron-relaunches-as-a-crypto-play\">back to life</a>, with a fresh website, newspaper ads, and billboard displays in its prior hometown of Houston. An account with the name Enron subsequently <a href=\"https://x.com/Enron/status/1863583974657863989\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">released a video on X</a> that announced the infamous company's comeback, as well as a countdown clock with a promise to introduce something special next week. It's got all the successful signs of every modern company, with monikers like \"shaping the future of sustainable energy,\" \"decentralized technology\" and around 20 trademark filings related to \"non-fungible tokens\" and \"cryptocurrency services.\"<br><br><em>Sound familiar?</em> It's somewhat of a flashback to the environment that saw many companies change their identity to cash in on the dot-com boom of the late 1990s and the first major crypto wave in 2017. Remember when AuctionWeb became eBay (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/EBAY\" title=\"eBay Inc.\">EBAY</a>)? Bioptix became Riot Blockchain (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/RIOT\" title=\"Riot Platforms, Inc.\">RIOT</a>)? And don't forget the <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/news/4338124-pony-ai-prices-ipo-at-13-per-ads\">AI suffixes</a> of the last several years. There might be some similarities this time around, with Bitcoin (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/BTC-USD\" title=\"Bitcoin USD\">BTC-USD</a>) recently skyrocketing to <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/news/4315597-bitcoin-tops-the-97000-level-a-closer-look-at-financial-conditions\">near the $100K-level</a>, while the Nasdaq (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/COMP:IND\" title=\"NASDAQ Composite Index\">COMP:IND</a>) continues to post near-daily record closing highs amid excitement over the artificial intelligence revolution.<br><br>\"Given historically elevated equity market valuations, prudent investors must remain highly selective and continue to manage risk proactively,\" <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/news/4356150-nasdaq-sp-and-dow-finished-mixed-as-treasury-yield-inversion-talks-resumed\">wrote</a> Seeking Alpha's Ahan Vashi, Investing Group Leader of <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/author/ahan-vashi#hasComeFromMpArticle=false#source=section%3Amain_content%7Cbutton%3Abody_link%7Cfirst_level_url%3Anews\">The Quantamental Investor</a>.<br><br><strong>The Crooked E:</strong> Upon further investigation, the new holder of the Enron trademark is Arkansas-based The College Company, which is owned by the co-creator of satirical group \"Birds Aren't Real.\" The new Enron website, which launched on its bankruptcy anniversary, further notes that \"THE INFORMATION ON THE WEBSITE IS FIRST AMENDMENT PROTECTED PARODY, REPRESENTS PERFORMANCE ART, AND IS FOR ENTERTAINMENT PURPOSES ONLY.\" A now-deleted video on X also teased a crypto offering, declaring that \"we do not have any token or coin (yet). Stay tuned, we are excited to show you more soon.\"</p> </div></div> <div class=\"wsb_section\"><div class=\"wsb_mb\"> <p class=\"wsb_bold\">What else is happening...</p> <p class=\"wsp-pb\">WSB survey results: The round-the-clock <a target=\"_blank\" data-stringify-link=\"https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSeSgvVIYyLAxZmWhH8z1v-x8mEJEXp3d8FyitT1FAoSWglSMw/viewanalytics\" delay=\"150\" data-sk=\"tooltip_parent\" href=\"https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSeSgvVIYyLAxZmWhH8z1v-x8mEJEXp3d8FyitT1FAoSWglSMw/viewanalytics\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">trading casino</a>.<br><br>Art Cashin, Wall Street icon and NYSE fixture, <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/news/4356600-art-cashin-prominent-nyse-figure-dies-83\">dies at 83</a>. <br><br>Analysts want 'radical change' at Intel (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/INTC\" title=\"Intel Corporation\">INTC</a>) <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/news/4356300-intel-board-should-consider-radical-change-with-new-ceo-analysts\">after CEO exit</a>.<br><br>Judge rejects <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/news/4356849-delaware-judge-again-rejects-musks-multi-billion-dollar-pay-package\">$56B payday</a> for <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/TSLA\">Tesla's</a> Musk; SpaceX <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/news/4357496-spacex-considers-tender-offer-that-boosts-valuation-to-350-billion-report\">worth $350B?</a><br><br>Fed's Waller leans toward supporting rate cut <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/news/4356043-feds-waller-leans-toward-december-rate-cut-sees-more-cuts-over-next-year\">in December</a>.<br><br>OpenAI CFO: Startup eyes introducing advertising to <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/news/4353580-openai-looks-to-add-advertising-to-artificial-intelligence-products-cfo-tells-ft\">AI products</a>.<br><br>NATO chief warns Trump of 'dire threat' from bad <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/news/4357502-nato-chief-trump-ukraine-peace-deal-russia-allies\">Ukraine deal</a>.<br><br>No confidence: French government set to collapse <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/news/4357563-france-government-no-confidence-vote-budget\">over budget</a>.<br><br>Super Micro (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/SMCI\" title=\"Super Micro Computer, Inc.\">SMCI</a>) jumps as internal review finds <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/news/4354335-super-micro-jumps-as-internal-review-finds-no-misconduct-to-replace-cfo\">no misconduct</a>. <br><br>Black Friday winners and losers: Sell-side analysts <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/news/4356040-black-friday-winners-losers-sell-side-weighs-in-on-black-friday-sales-results\">weigh in</a>.</p> <p class=\"wsb_bold\">Today's Markets</p> <p class=\"wsp-pb\"><b>In Asia, </b> Japan <span class=\"green\">+1.9%</span>. Hong Kong <span class=\"green\">+1%</span>. China <span class=\"green\">+0.4%</span>. India <span class=\"green\">+0.7%</span>.<br><b>In Europe, at midday, </b> London <span class=\"green\">+0.7%</span>. Paris <span class=\"green\">+0.2%</span>. Frankfurt <span class=\"green\">+0.3%</span>.<br><b>Futures at 6:30, </b> Dow <span class=\"red\">-0.1%</span>. S&amp;P flat. Nasdaq <span class=\"red\">-0.1%</span>. Crude <span class=\"green\">+1%</span> to $68.77. Gold <span class=\"green\">+0.3%</span> to $2,667.30. Bitcoin <span class=\"red\">-1%</span> to $94,890.<br><b>Ten-year Treasury Yield </b>+1 bp to 4.21%.</p> <p class=\"wsb_bold\">Today's Economic Calendar</p> <div class=\"before_last_paragraph-piano-placeholder\"></div>\n<p class=\"wsp-pb\"><span class=\"b\">10:00 AM</span> <a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/news/4354841-tuesdays-economic-calendar\">Job Openings and Labor Turnover Survey</a><br><span class=\"b\">11:00 AM</span> <a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/news/4354841-tuesdays-economic-calendar\"> Treasury Buyback Announcement (Preliminary)</a><br><span class=\"b\">12:35 PM</span> <a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/news/4354841-tuesdays-economic-calendar\">Fed\u2019s Kugler Speech</a><br><span class=\"b\">01:30 PM</span> <a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/news/4354841-tuesdays-economic-calendar\">Fed\u2019s Goolsbee Speech </a><br><br><a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/earnings/earnings-calendar#hasComeFromMpArticle=false#source=section%3Amain_content%7Cbutton%3Abody_link\">Companies reporting earnings today \u00bb</a> </p> </div></div> <div class=\"wsb_pt\"> </div> </div>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/674421/image_674421.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4741703-enron-is-back-from-dead-is", "pub_date": "2024-12-03 14:40:36"}, {"id": "4741695", "title": "XSW: Positioned For Long-Term Growth Amid AI And Rate Shifts", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1533018004/image_1533018004.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Two young software developers working in office\" data-id=\"1533018004\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1025px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1533018004/image_1533018004.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1533018004/image_1533018004.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1533018004/image_1533018004.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1533018004/image_1533018004.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1533018004/image_1533018004.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1533018004/image_1533018004.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1533018004/image_1533018004.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1533018004/image_1533018004.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">Luis Alvarez</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <h2>ETF Overview</h2> <p>SPDR S&amp;P Software &amp; Services ETF (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NYSEARCA:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/XSW\" title=\"SPDR\u00ae S&amp;P Software &amp; Services ETF\">XSW</a></span>) owns a portfolio of 140 software &amp; services stocks in the United States. The fund charges an expense ratio of 0.35%. This is higher than many other technology funds. For example, Vanguard Information</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1533018004/image_1533018004.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4741695-xsw-positioned-for-long-term-growth-amid-ai-and-rate-shifts", "pub_date": "2024-12-03 14:33:42"}, {"id": "4741708", "title": "No Market Misgiving On This Thanksgiving", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/894696738/image_894696738.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Candle stick graph chart with indicator showing bullish point or bearish point, up trend or down trend of price of stock market or stock exchange trading, investment concept.\" data-id=\"894696738\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/894696738/image_894696738.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/894696738/image_894696738.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/894696738/image_894696738.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/894696738/image_894696738.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/894696738/image_894696738.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/894696738/image_894696738.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/894696738/image_894696738.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/894696738/image_894696738.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">pookpiik/iStock via Getty Images</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>We\u2019ll see if there is any gravy left for investors during the last month of the year, but so far 2024 has been a satiating feast that has stuffed investors. There has been a cornucopia of items</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/894696738/image_894696738.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4741708-no-market-misgiving-this-thanksgiving", "pub_date": "2024-12-03 14:30:00"}, {"id": "4741691", "title": "High Tide: Strategic Expansions Drive Impressive Growth While Remaining Undervalued", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture><img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1403074050/image_1403074050.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Close-up of natural pattern on cannabis leaf\" data-id=\"1403074050\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1015px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1403074050/image_1403074050.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1403074050/image_1403074050.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1403074050/image_1403074050.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1403074050/image_1403074050.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/14030740